flowchart TD
    A["Approved weekly budget<br/>(token on record)"] --> B["Accounting disburses<br/>week's amount to Lead"]
    B --> C["User wallet block:<br/>amount at hand<br/>+ transaction history"]
    C --> D["Spend happens"]
    D --> E{"Bill photo attached?"}
    E -->|"no"| F["Transaction CANNOT be saved<br/>bill attachment is mandatory"]
    F --> D
    E -->|"yes"| G["Transaction recorded<br/>linked to bill + budget line"]
    G --> C
    G --> H["Tuesday: Lead tallies<br/>spend vs disbursed amount<br/>closes the week's accounts"]
    H --> I["Founder dashboard:<br/>budget vs actual<br/>per vertical, real time"]
    B --> I
